        tune: "Houghton",
        meter: "10s. 11s",
        key: "F Major",
        scripture: "FI ibukún fun Oluwa, iwọ ọkàn mi. Oluwa, Ọlọrun mi, iwọ tobi jọjọ: ọlá ati ọla-nla ni iwọ wọ̀ li aṣọ. Orin Dafidi 104:1",
